45:16.468 --> 45:34.864
into our VOQ mess and sat down across the table, and 
one naval officer crawled across the table trying

45:16.468 --> 45:34.864
to get to that guy. So I know what you mean when you 
talk about the old models. Well, I think that's

45:39.957 --> 45:41.719
what, too, is resources. I think individually for 
a student or family to say, I want to spend a summer

45:41.739 --> 45:53.410
or a semester abroad, there's a marginal cost to 
that, or it may preclude them from working. So

45:55.232 --> 46:05.121
making it feasible, and then certainly 
programmatically for a faculty or department to

45:55.232 --> 46:05.121
have a major role abroad, it's been pretty good. So 
getting the resource base in place to help that

46:05.624 --> 46:10.316
occur. There are some bureaucratic things as 
well. The state of Texas a couple of years ago had

46:20.693 --> 46:29.304
policies in place which discouraged faculty to 
be, I mean, to get your foreign travel approved and

46:20.693 --> 46:29.304
go away to the governor. Gee, Christmas for a state 
that, I mean, we are an international state

46:29.925 --> 46:35.572
already. What are we, the 11th largest economy in 
the world if we were a republic? In and of itself,

46:39.977 --> 46:40.999
yeah. Major ports and major international 
companies and just So we are a global state, but we

46:46.276 --> 46:50.062
don't always recognize it. But it's coming, and I 
think we've got a role to educate the state and our

46:51.204 --> 47:01.181
legislature and others about what we are and what 
we can be as a state. What do you think A&M's great

47:02.163 --> 47:07.873
strengths are in this development? In the 
international? Yeah. Well, one, our graduates.

47:11.318 --> 47:14.844
Or that will not only carry us into the 
international, but just into the future. Into the

47:14.864 --> 47:15.444
future? Yeah. Well, that's the same answer. That 
would be, I think, our graduates. I think we are

47:20.472 --> 47:27.864
producing a good graduate that the external 
markets recognize. And those external markets

47:28.885 --> 47:33.693
are employers, they're graduate schools, 
they're professional schools. And I think our

47:34.815 --> 47:37.579
students are great.

